manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Heavy Duty Armor for LG Stylo 5 Case/ LG Stylo 5 Plus Case/ LG Stylus 5 2-Layer Full Body Protective Shell Highlights: 1. Heavy Duty Protective Armor for LG Stylo 5/ LG Stylo 5 Plus/ LG Stylus 5, provide heavy duty protection for your phone from scratches and drop in daily life 2. Unique Armor Design, dual layer with hybrid bumper, makes your phone with outstanding looking 3. Perfect fit phone case, precise cut-outs allow easy access to all features of the phone without removing the case How to Install Step 1: Grab the Anti- Dust Plug and pull out the Rubber Layer. Take off the Rubber Layer, and then separate the hard inner shell into two parts. Step 2: The hard inner shell: Take apart the front shell&back shell by opening the slots on the sides. Step 3: Each inner shell device has button ports. According to the arrow lift the front and back shell carefully. Put your phone in a hard shell. Step 4: Put the Rubber Layer back on the hard shell. (Note: Make sure every slot on the hard shell is snapped on) Step 5: Press the edges of it and make sure it's matched with hard shell. Package included: 1 x Heavy Duty Protective Armor for LG Stylo 5 Warm Tips: 1.This item NOT include screen protector. 2.When using this product, it is not suitable to use a thicker tempered glass protective film(thin protective film can be used) !!! Otherwise, the screen protector may be damaged during the wearing of the phone case. 3.This product has raised edges around the screen, which can effectively protect the mobile phone screen, please rest assured to buy. 4.If you have any questions about the product, we are happy to assist.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is the first case my daughter has not taken off her phone for an extended amount of time. She is constantly breaking her screen. This has held up well and has protected her phone after multiple drops. I would buy it again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Durabilty and texture is great
reviews.reviewText: Does not come with a screen protector. The case overall is great. Clea m lines and the raised edge around the screen and camera provide great protection. Can buy multiple cases if you want to mix/match colors. I am good with the gray/blue. The case is tricky to figure out at first (for me anyway)it seemed like just two pieces arrived however the inside piece comes apart and be mindful when separating it because it is tight and the clips could break.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and attractive
reviews.reviewText: This appears to be a very sturdy case. All the buttons are usable and the hole for the fingerprint detector is large enough that my finger works with it. There is a very thorough installation Guide. The only quibble I have with the instructions is in step 3, during which you separate the top and bottom of the case. I found that I needed a small flat-blade screwdriver to open two of the clips.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 5, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Overall great case!!!
reviews.reviewText: So I purchased 2 of these cases so that I could have a color combination that I'd like. I ove purple but am not crazy about pink so I thought the blue with the purple would fit me and it does. Visually the case is awesome. It is built like an otterbox defender. Materials do feel different but seem like it will be protective in the even of a drop. Buttons work good and worked well with a glass screen protector. It is quite hard to open the inner shell. My main issue is like others have said, the pen is nearly impossible to remove with this case. I have nails and it takes me several tries to remove it.
